Ignore the comparisons to 'Kick Ass'.  This movie is far more inventive in its take on the 'no-super-powers-superhero'- genre.  Plenty of dark humor, over the top violence, and an ending which does not fit the typically American 'happily ever after' mold.  

I give the movie an 8 or 9
